sequenceDiagram
  participant UI as Workflow editor
  participant SA as Server Action
  participant DB as Neon
  participant T as Trigger.dev
  participant S as Stagehand
  participant B as Browserbase
  participant E as Resend
  UI->>SA: id and current graph
  SA->>SA: Clerk auth and graph/plan validation
  SA->>DB: save graph snapshot
  SA->>T: trigger run-workflow with workflow tag
  T->>DB: load organization-scoped graph
  T->>T: topological sort connected nodes
  loop Each node
    T-->>UI: metadata status update
    alt Browser node
      T->>S: execute node
      S->>B: browser/model operation
    else Email node
      T->>E: send email
    end
  end
  T-->>UI: final output and session ID

